{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">'Pieces of the Past' is a cute, sentimental adventure where you restore family keepsakes to uncover touching stories. Blend puzzle-solving with the joy of preserving memories in this delightful journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Repair and clean 4 items in the demo and experience a portion of the story with each item restored!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/extras/unravel_the_past.png?t=1729163456\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the life of Lily, a young adult gifted with the extraordinary ability of &quot;repairing memories.&quot; Fix broken items in this cozy, heartfelt puzzle adventure to uncover hidden family secrets. Explore themes of family, reconciliation, personal growth, and nostalgia in this captivating story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/extras/potp_virtualpet.gif?t=1729163456\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/extras/unlock_hidden_memories.png?t=1729163456\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilize Lily's unique skill to repair items and reveal the memories they hold. Each repaired item reveals a new piece of the family's history, offering insights into the motivations and experiences of each family member.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/extras/potp_operaglasses.gif?t=1729163456\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/extras/features.png?t=1729163456\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Memory Repair Mechanic:</strong> Fix broken items to uncover the memories within and piece together your family's history.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Emotional Storytelling:</strong> Dive deep into a narrative rich with themes of family, reconciliation, and personal growth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Detailed Environments:</strong> Explore a beautifully crafted antique shop filled with historical and atmospheric details.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Character-driven Experience:</strong> Witness Lily's journey of understanding and healing as she confronts the past.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Gameplay:</strong> Engage with a variety of items and puzzles to unlock new memories and advance the story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/extras/potp_artist_box.gif?t=1729163456\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join Lily in Pieces of the Past, where every repaired item brings a new revelation, and every</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">memory helps her rebuild the bonds of her family and shape her future. Rediscover the past </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">to shape your destiny.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729163456","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729163456","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729163456","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876650/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729163456","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_desc